      <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        <img src="/images/site_validator_scheduled_weekly.png" class="screenshot" alt="Scheduled validation screenshot" />
      </div>

      <p>
        Site Validator easily integrates with modern hosting platforms like <a href="http://docs.sitevalidator.com/continuous-validation/#example-netlify" target="_blank">Netlify</a>, <a href="http://docs.sitevalidator.com/continuous-validation/#example-heroku" target="_blank">Heroku</a> or <a href="http://docs.sitevalidator.com/continuous-validation/#example-cloud-66" target="_blank">Cloud 66</a> via webhooks, so you can set up automatic validations on your sites after a new version is deployed.
      </p>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px;">
